Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺害了休斯准將的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口徑是45mm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只使用了一發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁不住想誇犯人槍法好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從近距離開的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是女性也可以辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳所使用的槍的口徑是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,45mm口徑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳的子彈補充申請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡寫著一發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在申請書上也寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做愛德華·愛力克護衛的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五研究所…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所已經被封鎖了 應該是沒人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時並非沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳的主張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去找使用了的子彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所因為迷之爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了瓦礫之山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳用槍的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應是沒人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使想找子彈 也已經被埋在了瓦礫之下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 在作案時間前後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有證人說看到妳從現場離開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天正在放假 我在父母家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請向我的父母確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人以及親密朋友的證言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法作為不在場證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞·羅斯正在受審
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是長官也無法見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯斯軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐也來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 羅斯少尉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 實際上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上在第五研究所為了愛力克兄弟的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和少尉一起開了一槍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這件事情遞交了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒被接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備把少尉弄成犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}冰冷的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看 都是傷痕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常辛苦的旅程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳希望我們怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們從沒找我商量你們自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在休斯先生被殺的危險地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德和阿爾一直在戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一想 就覺得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 說不定會死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然從我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像爸爸和媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一想就覺得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 想讓你們放棄旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想讓你們恢復原來的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也想讓你們停止危險的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很溫柔的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 傷痕會變多的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（你在說什麼呢 真是的）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 又是報紙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有這麼點樂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法爾蔓准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從外線打的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接通馬斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 代碼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 這麼緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airam George Oliver 4649
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是那時的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有咬尾蛇刺青的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前台…報紙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞·羅斯少尉被斷定為殺害休斯准將的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐或少佐也許知道點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是小狗的項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是15歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是入侵者 快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖待著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒勁 沒勁 沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有沒有幹勁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不能砍就是無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 槍不起作用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我從這裡放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從清國來的非法入境者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這麼大老遠跑來真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把我放出去我就幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間和你玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說哪個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東邊的清國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈囉 甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五研究所的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能記得真讓我高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是每次看到右手被槍打的洞就會想起那時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害休斯的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報紙可是寫著確定是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣下去肯定是被套上罪名接受槍決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要仔細調查的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是等著被亂槍射死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和我一起逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二選一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外沒有選擇了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爸爸 媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好做好護衛 你這個笨蛋骨頭鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 氣勢不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是要膽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知市內全區
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞·羅斯越獄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有兇惡的共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即抓捕歸案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抵抗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許射殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多問 跑就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連麟也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我要問的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那邊的胡同裡一直走就能逃到倉庫街
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉著那裡的黑暗應該能逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉 休斯中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 憲兵來了的話 會被射殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 羅斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗亞·羅斯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 一線眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…麟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和那種傢伙在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會被羅斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對長官出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掂量一下自己有幾斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙把羅斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有令 射殺越獄的瑪麗亞·羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫僅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於隱瞞休斯之死的事情 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別對命令提出異議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得要求解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實地遵從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說明一下這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面應該有令 如果抵抗就可以射殺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為抵抗了 所以殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說准將是你的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓羅斯少尉越獄的不會是你的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了親手燒死她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要主觀地判斷事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒把休斯准將的死訊告訴你們 真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全到齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾克斯醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷實在太嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從勉強留下的牙齒治療痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以斷定這個人是瑪麗亞·羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是過份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個美人弄成了炭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你對她有很深的仇恨呢 馬斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報了仇 滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到伊修瓦爾戰的英雄會對一個小姑娘下這樣的毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 這次我的部下做了非常不該的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到羅斯少尉會殺人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個很誠實 很認真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有同情心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是疲勞積累得太多了 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經住過東部 那裡不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有都會的喧囂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且美人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古漂亮地替摯友報了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了讓大佐安分的作戰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗把餌吃了也是不錯的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他似乎引起了其他人的不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會被部下拋棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假申請
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擅自出門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被發現了的話 不知道大佐會怎麼教訓我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來的時候沒有被人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被兇惡的犯人抓住的可憐軍人 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 從剛才開始你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼煙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 把不認識的人帶來 你到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 真讓我們好找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人變多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉莎白 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你經常給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常偷懶的話會惹你那可怕的副官生氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 她休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托這個福 我能往妳那裡打電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉休假後馬上就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監護人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到了這裡以後一直沒有休假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多想拿個假期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近迷上了釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然幹什麼 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 你的機械鎧壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是重大事態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須馬上修理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責把你送到利塞布爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回利塞布爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 阿爾 聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太顯眼了 請留在中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 馬上就準備火車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這也是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個男人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壯少佐和愛德華·愛力克坐上火車了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來礙事的人就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見了拘留所襲擊犯的目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是犯人的畫像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和火焰之大佐有聯繫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 可能性很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 他不僅逃得很快而且藏得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人 大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手的話 有這個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 該你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劊子手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的真實都在克塞魯克塞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在漸漸腐朽消亡之城市的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂拭了少年的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八話 渺小人類的傲慢手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類喲 升起反擊的狼煙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:06.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}純白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:12.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:24.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:30.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:36.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:43.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:59.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:33.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:44.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這樣描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上塗鴉的花也會搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:55.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫長的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:01.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去與獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:08.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:16.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也好  痛苦也好  都將化為恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃照亮明天的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:27.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起小手  兩個人一起創造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:32.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜尋星塵與光芒四射的永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:38.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 那天也許還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季節依然在不斷地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有點迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:52.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:56.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}請讓我維持到永遠


